title: Virus Structure
description: An illustration of a virus, showing its outer envelope and internal structure. The virus has a spherical shape with spikes protruding from its surface, and a geometric core that contains genetic material represented by a wavy line.

title: Rabbit in Grass
description: A small rabbit sitting on lush green grass, with its ears perked up and a curious expression.

title: Wheat Field
description: A close-up view of green wheat plants in a field, showcasing the tall, slender stalks and developing wheat heads.

title: Osprey in Flight
description: An osprey is soaring above a body of water, clutching a fish in its talons. The bird has a white head and underbelly with dark brown wings and back. The background features a calm blue sea, enhancing the scene of the bird in action.

title: Lush Green Tree
description: A large, leafy tree with a broad canopy, standing on a grassy hill. The tree has a thick trunk and branches that extend outward, creating a dense area of foliage. The background features a clear sky, suggesting a bright and sunny day.

title: Immune Response Illustration
description: An illustration depicting the immune response process. It shows various cells interacting with viruses, represented by small spherical shapes with spikes. The cells are depicted in shades of blue and purple, with arrows indicating the flow of the immune response.
